#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Project Dev Tools
=================

Install:
  just install                         Install tools and dependencies
  just install tools                   Install tools from just.yaml into .tools
  just install deps                    Install Elixir and Node dependencies
  just install deps npm:<pkg> <version> --app <app>
                                       Add <pkg>@<version> to a Node app
  just install deps hex:<pkg> <version> --app <app>
                                       Add <pkg>@<version> to an Elixir app

Remove:
  just remove                          Show remove commands
  just remove deps                     Remove Elixir and Node dependencies
  just remove deps npm                 Remove node_modules only
  just remove deps hex                 Remove Elixir deps only
  just remove deps npm:<pkg> --app <app>
                                       Remove <pkg> from a Node app
  just remove deps hex:<pkg> --app <app>
                                       Remove <pkg> from an Elixir app

Check:
  just check specs [PATH...]           Check TLA+, Alloy, and OpenAPI specs
  just check types [PATH...]           Typecheck TypeScript apps under paths
  just check knip                      Check unused files, dependencies, and exports

Test:
  just test [PATH...]                  Run tests for selected apps

Build:
  just build [PATH...]                 Build or compile selected apps

Database:
  just migrate db                      Run Phoenix database migrations
  just reset db                        Drop, recreate, migrate, and seed the database

Dev:
  just dev [PROCESS...]                Run devservers with process-compose
  just dev --dry-run                   Validate process-compose.yaml without starting servers

Lint:
  just lint [PATH...]                  Lint Elixir, JS, TS, and CSS paths

Format:
  just format [PATH...]                Format JS, CSS, Elixir, and repo tooling paths
  just format --check [PATH...]        Check JS, CSS, Elixir, and repo tooling paths
EOF
